org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.browser

Class IconPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.browser.IconPool

  • public class IconPool
extends Object
    This class is used as a cache containing the icons that are used by the BrowserController to update the nodes. It keeps some icons associated with some entry types, to suffixes, to the root node, etc.

      • getIcon

        public ImageIcon getIcon(SortedSet<String> objectClasses,
                         int modifiers)
        If objectClass is null, a default icon is used.
        Parameters:
        objectClasses - the objectclass values of the entry for which we want an icon.
        modifiers - the modifiers associated with the entry (if there was an error, if it is a referral, etc.).
        Returns:
        the icon corresponding to the provided object classes and modifiers.
